dcterms:description: The DeepMind Mathematics Dataset consists of synthetically generated math problems covering a range of problem types including: Numbers, comparison, measurement, arithmetic, algebra, polynomials, calculus, and probability. The dataset provides the problems in the form of question-answer pairs represented as ASCII text.
dcterms:title: DeepMind Mathematics Dataset

dcterms:description: Various subsets of modules from the DeepMind Mathematics Dataset were used to evaluate model performance in a reinforcement learning context, focusing on modules that have composed counterparts.
dcterms:title: Various subsets of modules from the DeepMind Mathematics Dataset
